  "title": "反对双重思想",
  "image_width": 3585,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"4MEH1sA1\">这场达特茅斯-普林斯顿的比赛给我们带来一个启示：我们的大部分推理过程实际上是在事后合理化——我们编造故事，让自己当前的观点显得更加连贯和有道理，但这并不一定能提高观点的准确性。<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Against-Rationalization-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《反对合理化》</a><sup data-text=\"反对合理化\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/30664297001\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>系列探讨了这一问题，而<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Against-Doublethink-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《反对双重思想》</a>（关于自我欺骗）和<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Seeing-With-Fresh-Eyes-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《用新眼光看问题》</a>（关于挑战我们识别与预期和假设不符的证据的能力）系列则对此进行了进一步阐述。</p><p data-pid=\"MSuZ-5YM\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Rationality-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《理性：序言》</a><sup data-text=\"理性：序言\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827867654\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/30666103864\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">单重思想</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32609362607\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">双重思想（选择带有偏见）</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1888562465278760704\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">不，真的，我欺骗了自己</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1896140514681664097\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">相信自我欺骗</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1901755155327747608\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">摩尔悖论</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1904119088730608373\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">别以为你能骗得了自己</a><hr/><p data-pid=\"nsBdiwVu\">上一篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/30421407549\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">黑暗面的认识论</a><p data-pid=\"whgczWIT\">下一篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/30666103864\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">单重思想</a><hr/><blockquote data-pid=\"DQpx9JUH\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 claude-3-opus，校对 <span class=\"nolink\">Jarrett Ye</span><br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Against-Doublethink-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Against Doublethink - Sequence</a></blockquote>",
